Coca-Cola Enterprises Inc said itfiled with the Securities and Exchange Commission aregistration statement covering 500 mln dlrs of debt.    The company said it plans to sell 250 mln dlrs of notes due1997 and an equal amount of debentures due 2017.    Proceeds will be used to refinance outstandingindebtedness, Coca-Cola Enterprises said.    The company named Allen and Co Inc as lead manager andMerrill Lynch Capital Markets and Salomon Brothers Inc asco-managers of the offerings. Reuter&#3;